            "sections": [
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "2672215"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "Design your own kingdom",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p>Narnia is a great place to visit! You can go there every time you read the Narnia books. But why not create your own fantasy kingdom?</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pick a good <strong>name</strong> for your kingdom.</li>\n<li>Draw a <strong>map</strong> of your kingdom. Label bodies of water, woods, roads, where your creatures live, where your castle is located.</li>\n<li>Design your own <strong>castle</strong>.</li>\n<li>What kind of <strong>creatures</strong> are there in your kingdom? <strong>Describe or draw</strong> them.</li>\n<li>Make a <strong>list of laws/rules</strong> that are important for your kingdom.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img alt=\"Afbeeldingsresultaat voor map of Narnia\" src=\"https://www.awesomestories.com/images/user/17e3ea69ae.jpg\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n"
                        }
                    ],
                    "sections": []
                },
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "2672217"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "Let's refresh our memories ",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<h2>Let's refresh our memories</h2>\n<p>Some of you have seen the movie, but some of you haven't. Let's refresh our memories/ let's take a sneak peek.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/LshOd31d-yE\" width=\"560\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Now in pairs, <strong>describe</strong> to each other, in English, what the book we are going to read will be about.</p>\n<h2> </h2>\n"
                        }
                    ],
                    "sections": []
                },
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "2672219"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "Reading : Narnia: The Lion, The Witch and the Wardrobe",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<ul>\n<li>First I will read the story to you, <strong>read along</strong> and pay attention to pronunciation.</li>\n<li>Now I would like you to <strong>read the story to the class</strong>, so beforehand you prepare assigned pages in pairs. Practise reading them in English and discuss in Dutch what happens at those pages.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.google.nl/url?sa=i&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;frm=1&amp;source=images&amp;cd=&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;docid=WfAArBt1CvhJ0M&amp;tbnid=nEJfoFtj4md75M:&amp;ved=0CAUQjRw&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmovies.disney.com%2Fthe-chronicles-of-narnia-the-lion-the-witch-and-the-wardrobe&amp;ei=aWyZU4-AHcXaPLCygMgM&amp;psig=AFQjCNHBlbgmpDn2EB4RJMbYB22u0TDwsQ&amp;ust=1402650016761658\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdnvideo.dolimg.com/cdn_assets/e30802d90755e019fd179e3452475a6bae0676c9.jpg\" class=\"height-403-pixels width-286-pixels\"/></a></p>\n"
                        }
                    ],
                    "sections": []
                },
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "2672221"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "Scenes in close up ",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<h2>Scenes in close up</h2>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>While the Pevensies run for their lives they meet a lot of creatures. They also meet Father Christmas who gives them presents.  After watching the scene <strong>draw</strong> the <strong>presents</strong> the Pevensies get <strong>and describe them</strong>. Also <strong>draw what you would like to get from Father Christmas for your Fantasy Kingdom and describe it.</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uvoJGjoLeiU\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uvoJGjoLeiU</a></p>\n<p>------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Before the Pevensies return to their old lives, they have to fight the White Witch. After watching the scene <strong>tell your neighbour if you are happy with the ending and why (not)?</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XacLk1XUZCo\" width=\"420\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<h2>Narnia: Prince Caspian</h2>\n<p>Years have passed\u2026.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/VqzYukVDqy4\" width=\"560\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Let's read</li>\n<li>In groups of 4 you <strong>read the story to each other</strong></li>\n<li>You<strong> answer each other's questions</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n"
                        }
                    ],
                    "sections": []
                },
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "2672224"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "And the lived happily ever after",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p><em>Lucy knew that only time would tell how the battle would end. But in her heart Lucy felt the strength of a Lion\u2026..</em><a href=\"http://pjustin.files.wordpress.com/2012/02/caspian-aslan.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://pjustin.files.wordpress.com/2012/02/caspian-aslan.jpg?w=300&amp;h=233\" class=\"height-233-pixels width-300-pixels\"/></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Finish the story</strong>. It's completely up to you how the story ends. So it doesn't have to end happily ever after\u2026..</p>\n<p> </p>\n"
                        }
                    ],
                    "sections": []
                }
            ]
        }
